Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.75,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}这就是  牵线人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:02.95,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}无法将心情传递给你
